Private Events
83 West and 29 North at 83 West are the PREMIER locations for your next private event in Cedar Key! With the BEST views and atmosphere in Cedar Key, you and your guests are sure to have an amazing event! Private Events are recommended for groups of 25+ guests depending on the type of event! We can help you host anything from a business conference to a full wedding and reception! For detailed Information and pricing for private events, fill out the form below and our events manager will be in contact with you as soon as possible! Please see detailed pricing below for both venues.
29 North is recommended for longer (4+hour), more intimate gatherings for larger groups, such as weddings and birthday bashes!
83 West (downstairs) is recommended for shorter, smaller gatherings, and more casual affairs such as reunions, rehearsal dinners, and everyday birthday celebrations!
We also offer special Corporate Pricing for Weekday Events. Please free to contact us about any of your event needs.
When considering if a private event is best for your large group or party, please keep in ind that we do not take reservations for regular dining, and groups larger than 8 will be asked to split between available tables at time of arrival.
Please Review Event Packages Below. To Learn More, or Book a Special Event, Please CALL US AT 352.543.5070 ext. 4 and leave a message detailing your inquiry and we will return your call on our next day of operation
